Class AdapterDetailsView

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iha.emulator.ui.panels.adapter.details.AdapterDetailsView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class AdapterDetailsView
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, AdapterDetailsPresenter.Display
    Class providing GUI components for "Adapter details panel". Part View of MVP design pattern. Contains methods invoked on user interaction with user interface. These methods call appropriate presenter method to process user interaction.

    Filip Sutovsky
